Check out this package from CVS to your CMSSW_2_1_8/src directory: (Note that you must name the 
directory "RootTuple" in your src directory in order for this to compile!!)
>cvs co -d Leptoquarks/RootTupleMaker UserCode/Leptoquarks/RootTupleMaker

Check out the packages needed for Jet Corrections:
>cvs co -r V01-06-05 CondFormats/JetMETObjects
>cvs co -r V01-08-10 JetMETCorrections/Configuration
>cvs co -r V02-09-00 JetMETCorrections/Modules

Check out teh packages for Electron ID and Isolation:
>cvs co -r V00-05-19 RecoEcal/EgammaCoreTools

Compile:
>scram b

Change the file name in roottuplemaker_cfg.py to point to your input file.
Run the RootTupleMaker:
>cmsRun roottuplemaker_cfg.py
